{"tid":931220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據報日本擬禁止政府採購華為及中興通訊產品","createTime":"2018-12-07T01:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T03:40:25.000Z","uid":173631,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4550ca7cd3b425b76454bedc3163274a87d994d","tid":931220,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432153-20181207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432153-20181207.htm&d=RGtujUXDJSHD%2FDnQ12ZO026tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e9f2f98c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432153-20181207.htm&h=5172834f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432153-20181207.htm</a><br />\n日本媒體報道指，日本將禁止政府向中國華為及中興通訊採購電訊產品，擔心發生情報洩漏及遭到網絡攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n日本讀賣新聞引述政府消息人士指，預計政府下周一修訂有關政府採購的內部規則，華為及中興將是禁止對象，但為免激怒中國，日本不太可能提及兩間公司。<br />\n<br />\n美國早前亦禁止政府採購華為設備，澳洲及新西蘭亦以國家安全為由不准5G網絡使用華為設備。英國電信本周三指，正撤走現有3G及4G移動網絡核心部分使用的華為設備，5G核心不再使用華為。"},{"pid":"7ea582f632b91455924b4792c520b4a67a2fcf54","tid":931220,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"益台灣廠商 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79aee0bf65d871c755d38b4d4c2b1301999b0545","tid":931220,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:47:48.000Z","msg":"重有聯想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b3c74d922299aa66cf351c534564dcca001dd5","tid":931220,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:57:44.000Z","msg":"民國復興條柒碌唔係話日本一直考慮緊華為5G咩？<br />\n出嚟講兩句？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cb36205c6d4cf30001d5177a99deb6cfa15140","tid":931220,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}